WEBVTT


00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:04.440
Jobs are available in Finland with visa sponsorship.

00:00:04.440 --> 00:00:05.700
Starwalkers,

00:00:05.720 --> 00:00:06.980
electricians,

00:00:07.160 --> 00:00:09.340
waiters and lots more.

00:00:09.360 --> 00:00:10.540
How to apply?

00:00:10.640 --> 00:00:13.300
On Google type go on Finland,

00:00:13.400 --> 00:00:15.020
click on the first link,

00:00:15.120 --> 00:00:17.200
click on see all open jobs.

00:00:17.200 --> 00:00:19.180
There are two ways to apply.

00:00:19.400 --> 00:00:21.440
These are the current job openings.

00:00:21.440 --> 00:00:23.280
To view a particular job,

00:00:23.280 --> 00:00:25.420
you simply click on the plus sign

00:00:25.720 --> 00:00:27.320
for this particular position,

00:00:27.320 --> 00:00:28.980
which is that of a waiter.

00:00:29.160 --> 00:00:31.180
Pay attention to the deadline

00:00:31.360 --> 00:00:33.780
and if it is full time or part time.

00:00:34.080 --> 00:00:35.400
If you're interested

00:00:35.400 --> 00:00:37.220
you click on the apply button

00:00:37.280 --> 00:00:39.360
or you can read the job description

00:00:39.360 --> 00:00:41.420
and exactly how to apply.

00:00:41.440 --> 00:00:44.420
To apply, click on apply for this job,

00:00:44.840 --> 00:00:47.280
feeling the basic information about yourself,

00:00:47.280 --> 00:00:48.720
your driver's license,

00:00:48.720 --> 00:00:49.800
your education,

00:00:49.800 --> 00:00:51.980
your country and your work experience

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:54.780
and at the end you click on send.

00:00:55.040 --> 00:00:56.600
The second method to apply

00:00:56.600 --> 00:00:58.720
is to send an open application.

00:00:58.720 --> 00:01:02.060
This case you're not applying for a specific job,

00:01:02.120 --> 00:01:03.980
you simply express your interest

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:06.300
and they will contact you with the suitable rule.

00:01:06.320 --> 00:01:07.280
Click on send,

00:01:07.280 --> 00:01:08.160
complete this form

00:01:08.160 --> 00:01:09.960
which is skills and experience

00:01:09.960 --> 00:01:11.960
and at the end click send.

00:01:11.960 --> 00:01:13.240
Repeat this process

00:01:13.240 --> 00:01:16.820
to find jobs in Finland with visa sponsorship.
